IMAPAccount speigad
Host imap.gmail.com
User speigad@umich.edu
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.emacs.d/.mbsyncpass.gpg"
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs *
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore speigad-remote
Account speigad

MaildirStore speigad-local
Path ~/.mail/speigad/
Inbox ~/.mail/speigad/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel speigad
Far :speigad-remote:
Near :speigad-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge None
SyncState *